###############################################################################
# GITIGNORE POLICY
# ================
# This repository commits CODE and DOCUMENTATION, not DATA.
# Rationale: data/ contains large market feeds and runtime artifacts that are
# - Regenerable from source (TrueFX API, Pine alerts, candle aggregation)
# - Local-only (development/testing artifacts)
# - Not shared across environments
#
# See data/README.md for detailed policy and regeneration instructions.
###############################################################################

# Python Environment
venv/
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.pytest_cache/

# Environment & Secrets (SECURITY)
.env
.env.local
ict_trading_system/.env
ict_trading_system/backend/.env

# Databases (Local only, not committed)
# Rationale: trading_system.db contains 49 real webhook signals ingested from
# TradingView Pine Script. This is state, not code. Each environment maintains
# its own signal history from live webhooks. See data/README.md.
*.db
*.sqlite3
trading_system.db
ict_trading_system/backend/alerts.db
data/databases/*.db

# Logs & Outputs (Runtime)
*.log
*.out
nohup.out
logs/
*.bak

# OS & Editor
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# .md files IGNORED EXCEPT in /docs folder (documentation is centralized)
*.md
!README.md
!PROJECT_STRUCTURE.md
!docs/**/*.md
!docs/*.md

# Build Artifacts
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
.eggs/

# Test Artifacts (but keep integration tests)
.coverage
htmlcov/
.pytest_cache/

# Generated temporary files
__init__.py  # Auto-generated, not essential
# Generated backtest artifacts (runtime outputs, not source)
results/*.json
results/*.md
!results/.gitkeep  # Keep directory in git

# Market Data & Generated Artifacts (NOT committed)
# Rationale:
# - data/raw/: TrueFX ticks (~34 MB) - downloadable from TrueFX API
# - data/processed/: Candles, signals, exports (~2 MB) - regenerable via scripts
# - data/databases/: SQLite DBs - built from live webhook ingestion
# Each environment generates its own data locally. See data/README.md for policy.
data/processed/
data/raw/
# EXCEPTION: Commit data/README.md (policy documentation)
!data/README.md
